    <p>The kitchen, which is of the highest catering standard, features:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Six burner gas catering range with oven</li>
        <li>Four ring electric cooker with oven</li>
        <li>Large hot cupboard</li>
        <li>Instant boiling water</li>
        <li>Freezer</li>
        <li>Large capacity refrigerator</li>
        <li>Twin serving hatches with electric shutters</li>
        <li>Crockery and cutlery for 150 diners</li>
        <li>Commercial dishwasher</li>
        <li>Ample stainless steel preparation surfaces</li>
    </ul>
