<p>The Hall has an audio visual system and free WiFi. So you are able to show wedding messages from abroad on the big electrically operated screen.</p>

<p>As the Hall has a full stage, rearrangement of tables after the wedding breakfast would facilitate dancing to a live band. 
    Alternatively, the in-house sound system can be used to play your own choice of music.</p>

